title: Decoy - Storm of the Century (2002) (Digital) (DR & Quinch-E
description:
Decoy - Storm of the Century (2002) (Digital) (DR & Quinch-Empire)



He's the champion of justice and fast one-liners, a green shape-shifting alien from the planet Nacrum whose primary purpose in life is to protect the innocent and to one-up his roommate in the an ongoing battle of pranks and bad jokes. All goes well until a subterranean encounter with a long-forgotten threat changes Decoy's life and threatens the friendship with his only ally on the planet: his best friend. Faced with identity crisis of cosmic proportions, lovable alien Decoy much team up with his buddy, rookie copy Bobby Luck, to battle meteorological and psychological disaster
